text: Kannarin Thawornsak (, born May 27, 1997), is a Thai professional footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder for Thai League 1 club Port. ==International career== In 2020, He played the 2020 AFC U-23 Championship with Thailand U23. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Thai footballers Category:Thai League 1 players Category:Bangkok Christian College F.C. players Category:Port F.C. players Category:Ratchaburi Mitr Phol F.C. players Category:Sisaket F.C. players Category:Suphanburi F.C. players
